OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FEx-minister: I wish I asked
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fmore about Post Office     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Labour's Pat McFadden has said he      
OL,6, wishes he had asked more questions     
OL,7, about the Post Office when he was a    
OL,8, minister after the IT scandal emerged. 
OL,10,FMr McFadden was the minister in charge 
OL,11,Fof postal affairs from 2007 for around 
OL,12,Fthree years.                           
OL,14,FThe shadow minister recently claimed he
OL,15,Fcould not recall the scandal being     
OL,16,Fraised with him during that time.      
OL,18,FHowever, he told the BBC that he had   
OL,19,Fgone back and checked, admitting: "It  
OL,20,Fdid cross my desk."                    
